reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent portable battery for traveling
reviews.reviewText: I have taken this on many trips in the past year. It does lose power somewhat quickly when you use it to charge your phone. But that must just be par for the course with these items. I do like that it has a percentage number on the battery. To show you how much is left before it needs charging. It charges best when it's plugged into a wall outlet. I don't recommend charging it in a car as it doesn't charge that well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I use this when I'm out and about and it works great! It can charge my devices pretty quickly and holds a charge for a while too!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lifesaver during overseas travel
reviews.reviewText: This is a fantastic multi-use charger. Travelled overseas with Android and iPhone users, so this charger worked perfectly for all of our needs. I bought a portable hot spot during the trip and this handy dandy little charger worked on that as well. It's a nice slim, streamlined design, which made it easy to keep in my purse. I also love the LED display, which showed me how much battery life I had left.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This has helped me in a pinch a couple times and I love it, it takes a while to charge but the charge lasts a while and you can completely recharge your phone with one full battery and then have some left for next time

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best Portable Charger Ever
reviews.reviewText: This charger is so worth it especially for the price. It has so many different cables attached to it and it lasts forever. Would definitely recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Holds charge for a long time
reviews.reviewText: This battery pack is so convenient. I love having the charging cables built in and stored securely on the back side. It holds its charge for a long time when its not being used. I've recommended it to friends.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Charge on the go
reviews.reviewText: Love this compact phone charger. My favorite part is that I can still use my phone while the charger is attached. I carry it is my purse for charge on the go and appreciate how lightweight it is and how quickly it charges. The price is right for giving it as a gift too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect portable charger
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for a battery pack to power my GoPro in remote locations and this one has worked perfect. Small, sturdy and full of power. Have left it out overnight for a timelapse and no issues and with +30% of battery left.

The colour was great / different compared to what’s available. Really like the fact that there’s a digital display of how much battery is left in comparison to other portable battery packs. The product has a nice feel to it and it isn’t heavy. Purchased during the Black Friday sale and definitely worth it.
Works great for what I need. Charging my phone, headphones and powering the fan on my inflatable Trex costume. Charges slowly on the wrong voltage, but the proper voltage works great.

I've had this unit for a while. It worked fine in terms of charging quickly and then charging the device. But seems temperamental depending on the cord you use. Unfortunately when I traveled with it I used a different card and it didn't charge my phone. This was really disappointing. So I would just be careful with the charger that you use. I went back to use the old charger and it's been working fine since.

reviews.reviewTitle: Battery capacity is as advertised, fast charging time, battery enclosure build quality is good.
reviews.reviewText: Got this at a discounted price for $20 during Black Friday.1. Battery capacity is as advertised 10000mAh.2. Can charge 3 devices at the same time.3. It has a battery level indicator with actual numbers.4. The battery enclosure plastic is of good quality and texturized for better grip.5. Comes with a little pouch to carry the battery around.
Perfect for a trip.Took average 20-25% of batterie to get a phone to near full charge.Size feels like a phone in pants pocket.Shipping was fast.
